title: Double Rail Medium Duty Z Rack Garment Rack
description: Orange Z-base Only. 350 lb load capacity. 70 in. of vertical hang space. 60 in. of horizontal hang space. 63 in. base - 14 gauge steel. 77 in. uprights. Solid and balanced construction is critical for any storage rack. Our model is built with balance in mind so that the second row of clothing sits over the other and within the support of the wheels. The uprights extend 73 in. high, and the second rail is adjustable so that it sits wherever you decide is best.
